title: God is Your Source
itunes:title: God is Your Source
description:
God has given us resources, our jobs, our families, our relationships, but we cannot mistake the resources from the Source. God is our Source and His supply never runs short. We can live free from the pressure of people pleasing, confident in the assurance that God will supply all of our needs according to Christ Jesus.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
